tyle: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> wrote at the time</a>:</p><blockquot=
e><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">This is the peak of meme stocks. Bed Bath &a=
mp; Beyond sold 50 million shares a week for three months with, as far as I=
 can tell, no story, no plan, nothing but =E2=80=9Ca troubled financial sit=
uation and nostalgia value.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0Bed Bath saw that its retail shar=
eholders wanted to throw their money away, and that its sophisticated lende=
rs wanted to get their money back, and realized that there was a trade to b=
e done that would make everyone, temporarily, happy. So it did the trade.</=
p></blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But why stop there? By April,=
